Package org.eclipse.emf.compare.rcp.ui.mergeviewer.item.provider

Interface IMergeViewerItemProvider

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IOptionalProvider
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CompareAccessorMergeViewerItemProvider
    public interface IMergeViewerItemProvider
extends IOptionalProvider
    The contract for providers responsible for determining root elements in merge viewers. Typically these are IMergeViewerItems but they not necessarily have to be.
